@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图22  票据状态流转图

[*] --> UNUSED : 订单 PAID 后生成

UNUSED --> CHECKED_IN : 检票员核销
UNUSED --> INVALID : 管理员作废
UNUSED --> REFUNDED : 退票 (后续扩展)

note right of UNUSED
  含票号 + 二维码模拟码
  对应一个 schedule_seat
end note

note right of CHECKED_IN
  写入 checkin_record
  不可再次检票
end note

CHECKED_IN --> [*]
INVALID --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]
@enduml
